room_title: Escape room " Lost Cabin" by Puzzle Room Reno in Reno
review: This was the most fun I have had in a long time! The puzzle was so well done! Erik was such a wonderful host. We all loved it and we even broke the record in the "Lost Cabin " room. This is a must do!
